text: Nigeria’s Vice President launchs 60-day plan to improve business climate Reuters ABUJA Feb 21 Nigeria’s Vice President Yemi Osinbajo has launched a 60-day action plan to improve the business climate in Africa’s biggest economy struggling with recession, his office said on Tuesday. “There are improvements which we expect to see at …
